{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99706-ji-wu-de-moli","title":"基乌的魔力","description":"基乌能看到其他人看不到而令人兴奋的东西-飞行火箭和在黑板上游泳的鱼。奶奶带着基乌去看眼科医生了解她的魔力。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Shrujana Shridhar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99706-ji-wu-de-moli"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722813/size3/196de06440ab4625dccdce4e70396bd7.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722813/size6/196de06440ab4625dccdce4e70396bd7.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54036/size6/5efaa721b68913a27ad713f5f4fad159.jpg","text":"基乌上学迟到了。\n但她找不到她的红色瓶子。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54034/size6/350897a3f5f842acb1db9c0b6b42d3cd.jpg","text":"那是她的瓶子吗？\n还是一个火箭？","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54035/size6/4cbcec720131dea002975ab3dd66bde3.jpg","text":"基乌看着黑板，而想着,\n“那些是在海里游的鱼吗？”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54039/size6/9530c841552504050998a81793b6c09e.jpg","text":"基乌盯着鞋上的一滴绿色斑点，想着,\n“这很粘，看起来像果冻。 难道是一只青蛙吗?\n”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54041/size6/75077baa23a49e5b6cec15755ab4e745.jpg","text":"基乌跑着回家跟奶奶说,\n“我有神奇的魔力！ 我能看到别人看不到的东西 。\n”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54040/size6/e47fdc864da30ed940f3bf75457a7db0.jpg","text":"奶奶点点头而问，“那么我们是不是应该去眼科医生那，\n告诉她你的魔力？”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54048/size6/4d8f2af0c8625bb09ebdaab671a0638b.jpg","text":"8/17","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54043/size6/a107ab415439a32a70d25fb0caf1e8c4.jpg","text":"尼基塔医生拿了一张图表给基乌看。\n“那些蚂蚁正在图上行进吗?\n”\n基乌问道。","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54044/size6/4f343584b490fc803894c1b71ab331e5.jpg","text":"尼基塔医生帮基乌试戴眼镜。\n最大的蚂蚁变成了E.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54045/size6/60f2b8b8cc388195e7a3a919b3e091e2.jpg","text":"“难道我失去我的魔法了吗，医生?”基乌问道。\n \n“闭上眼睛做梦。 你的魔法会回来的, ”\n尼基塔医生说。","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54046/size6/260cb2f49d5fb658d5884b498d3ddf8d.jpg","text":"“基乌，你想要什么颜色的眼镜？”奶奶问道。\n“给我绿色的吧,”基乌笑着说。","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54050/size6/d342ef6053f183ea768018375235306a.jpg","text":"眼镜的情况\n基乌没有戴眼镜而看不太清楚。\n你能帮她吗？","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54088/size6/1a54573d101024807875930ef8bb7f6c.jpg","text":"以下的形状叫什么呢？","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54089/size6/17beac1d10f2740dcc8b51e6e394dca1.jpg","text":"花里面藏了多少圆图？","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54090/size6/b6998824a90b77283630c60fb3c6d3ad.jpg","text":"你在这颗星星上看到了几个三角形？","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54091/size6/d638f581ad95a6d211caa256f9c33fdf.jpg","text":"窗户里有几个方块？","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":38}}